==English==
===Pronunciation===
*/kæməkaːziː/
===Etymology===
From Japanese [[神風]] (かみかぜ, kamikaze), ''divine wind''.

===Noun===
'''kamikaze'''

#an [[attack]] requiring the [[suicide]] of the one carrying it out, esp. when done with aircraft.
#one who makes such an attack

